measurements.description: Thirty-seven starry flowers and five buds well arranged on three arching up to 70.2-cm inflorescences; sepals and petals light chartreuse overlaid mahogany, striped and blotched darker mahogany mid-rib; lip creamy white, blushed light yellow centrally, side lobes spotted burgundy, mid lobe darker burgundy blotches; column creamy white blushed red-brown distally, anther cap white; substance firm; texture matte.
